e bronzes in the Olympics that followed his precocious debut but clambered to the summit of the podium alongside Lee, who announced he would miss the Games owing to spinal surgery in March, to grab one of Britain's first golds in Japan.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2814, \"end\": 2817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9275772170506085, \"rank\": 0.07756974931448557, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2906, \"end\": 2913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9706010343634122, \"rank\": 0.030286466120803282, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5533625544731614, \"rank\": 0.6683322276298479, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"three consecutive bronzes\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2726}, {\"ngram\": \"his precocious debut\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"the summit\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2789}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"spinal surgery\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He and Williams, 24, will bid to defend that title in Paris but Daley admits the pressure is off as he hopes to make more history at La Defense Arena.\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2993, \"end\": 2998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999887359082, \"rank\": 1.1264182945921007e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Williams\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2954}, {\"ngram\": \"that title\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3008}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"more history\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Beijing, London and Rio I tortured myself as I wanted to do so well so badly,\\\" added Daley, who is married to Dustin Lance Black and has another son, Phoenix Rose, aged one.\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3095, \"end\": 3102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999994711288, \"rank\": 5.289699553562092e-10, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3104, \"end\": 3110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999961303958407, \"rank\": 3.859972156163518e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 3205, \"end\": 3223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}, {\"begin\": 3245, \"end\": 3252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9782978168497066, \"rank\": 0.02217008685038898, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}, {\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9999990428063972, \"rank\": 7.89768897413377e-07, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3118}, {\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3185}, {\"ngram\": \"another son\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Tokyo, I finally got to a point with perspective that no matter how I did, I am going home to a family that loved and supported me.\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tokyo\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time around, I have got my gold medal, I have done everything I have wanted to do in the sport so I am going to enjoy it, soak in the atmosphere, look around and think: 'Wow - this is what I have worked [for] all of my life.'\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my gold medal\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3448}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3505}, {\"ngram\": \"the atmosphere\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, I 